          "description": "An eerie feeling overwhelms your senses as you enter this room. Shivering torches form dancing shadows on the wall all around you. The ground looks like stone, but seems to cushion your feet as you walk on it. Everywhere you look, you see piles of books stacked on each other. Near the back of the room, is a wooden desk with a chair sitting behind it. A set of stairs lead back up to the tower.",
